
# GO Transit Display Board - Graphic Charter

## Brand Colors

Primary Colors:
- Black: #000000 (Background, Headers)
- White: #FFFFFF (Text, Content)
- Red: #FF0000 (Delays, Cancellations)
- Blue: #0052A5 (Accessibility Indicators)

Status Colors:
- Delayed: #FF0000
- On Time: #FFFFFF
- Platform: #FFFFFF

## Typography & Spacing

Font Family: Polaris (Custom Font)
Variations:
- Polaris Bold: Headers, Important Information
- Polaris Medium: Navigation, Subheaders
- Polaris Light: Body Text, General Content

Font Sizes and Spacing:
- Station Name: 2.625rem (42px)
- Time Display: 3rem (48px)
- Schedule Headers: 2.25rem (36px)
- Schedule Rows: 2.25rem (36px)
- Line Height: 1.5
- Letter Spacing: -0.02em

## Layout Elements

### Header Section
- Position: Fixed at top
- Height: 6rem (96px)
- Padding: 1.5rem 2rem
- Background: Black (#000000)
- Border Bottom: 0.125rem (2px) solid var(--go-green)
- Z-index: 100

### Logo Section
- Position: Left side of header
- Height: 2.5rem (40px)
- Margin Right: 1.25rem (20px)
- Aspect Ratio: Auto

### Station Info
- Position: Center of header
- Icon Size: 2.25rem (36px)
- Name Size: 2.625rem (42px)
- Letter Spacing: -0.02em
- Margin: 0.5rem 0

### Time Display
- Position: Right side of header
- Size: 3rem (48px)
- Color: #FFFFFF
- Letter Spacing: -0.02em
- Font Weight: Bold
- Margin Left: auto

### Schedule Grid
- Display: Grid
- Grid Template: repeat(4, 1fr)
- Column Gap: 1rem (16px)
- Row Gap: 0.5rem (8px)
- Padding: 1rem 0.8rem
- Border Bottom: 0.0625rem (1px) solid #333
- Font: Polaris Light, 2.25rem (36px)

### Control Panel
- Max Width: 50rem (800px)
- Margin: 2rem auto
- Padding: 1.25rem
- Form Elements Gap: 1rem
- Button Padding: 0.625rem 1rem

## Responsive Breakpoints

Large Screens (>75rem/1200px):
- Default sizes apply

Medium Screens (≤75rem/1200px):
- Station Name: 2.25rem (36px)
- Time Display: 2.25rem (36px)
- Schedule Text: 1.75rem (28px)

Small Screens (≤48rem/768px):
- Station Name: 1.75rem (28px)
- Time Display: 1.75rem (28px)
- Schedule Text: 1.5rem (24px)
- Grid: 1fr 1fr 1fr 0.5fr
- Padding: 1rem

## Accessibility

- Minimum Contrast Ratio: 4.5:1
- Focus Indicators: 0.125rem (2px) solid outline
- Alert Messages: Background #FF0000, White text
- Interactive Elements:
  - Minimum Touch Target: 2.75rem (44px)
  - Focus Ring Offset: 0.25rem (4px)
